Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 比想象中还要难登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和日向拼命向山顶前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连葵和枫那份一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(1037,215)}「再也不要了！！」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头疼怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好一点了 不过还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 马上就要天亮了 日出怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得 稍微努力一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面再穿上些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我跟妈妈借来了羽绒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是山顶的鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 日出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜色渐明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都在看着同一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉仿佛是一个整体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出太震惊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了真是太好了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…为什么我的身体动不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心 我不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们到山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下了山就会好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上也下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急的 机会难得 绕火山口一圈怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕火山口一圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕火山口走上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个半小时到两个小时左右就能绕一圈 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先下到五合目 到了再给你们打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 我的脚很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 吃了便当以后 去绕火山口一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉酱汤也好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山很饿肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的消耗能量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要走很久呢 好好补充能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚才还很黑看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有岩石 云彩 和天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在天空散步一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉风好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像仙人掌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想写给葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少把我现在的心情告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也来写
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头和脚都很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不走的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不露出不悦的表情 却和我在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我给你添了那么大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终点还在很远的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算走啊走啊 也完全无法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事还要继续到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「还有多远呢」你还是不要总想着这样的事比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越想越总是无法到达哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脑袋放空 专心走路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什么时候就会到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我明明这么痛苦却要登山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还会来到这种地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚好累 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑峰 3776米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是日本的 最高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 我享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 到了吗 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐巴士还有时间 去看看土特产怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样呀 下次来请让我乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看土特产吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山也很辛苦啊 脚都快断了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过刻印全都刻上了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个 葵想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我买给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 巴士快来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家里联系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了那么多任性的话 一定会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你都没联系我 我好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的声音是怎么了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我等下要去坐巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记跟你联系了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 你努力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体没事吧 能回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 我明明让你这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道该做出什么表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太惊奇了 富士山不愧是世界的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头也疼 脚也疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累 我再也不想留下这种回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)\pos(919,530)}未完待续
